     2	
     3	Uses jsonschema if available; falls back to typed-model validation for
     4	``pam-environment.v1`` only when jsonschema is missing.
     5	
     6	Phase 0 (PAM parity program): every packaged ``*.v1`` family resolves via
     7	``schema: <family>.v1`` (or legacy ``version`` + ``name`` for PAM). See
     8	``docs/PAM_PARITY_PROGRAM.md``.
