    12	| `main.py` | 1200+ | Click commands (`validate`, `plan`, `diff`, `apply`, `import`, `export`, `report …`, `live-smoke`) + exit-code orchestration. `EXIT_CHANGES == EXIT_SCHEMA == 2` (intentional overload — see comment + DOR). |
    13	| `_report/` | — | `dsk report` wrappers: `runner.py` (batch subprocess), `common.py` (JSON envelope + UID fingerprints), `password.py`, `compliance.py`, `security_audit.py`. |
    14	| `renderer.py` | 104 | `RichRenderer` — human tables for plan/outcomes/diff. Snapshot-tested in `tests/test_renderer_snapshots.py`. |
    15	
