    17	
    18	| Verb | Exit codes | Machine flag | JSON contract |
    19	|---|---|---|---|
    20	| `validate` | 0/2/3/5 | `--emit-canonical`, `--json`, `--online` | `mode` + `family` + stage list (`schema_only`, `pam_full`, `vault_offline`, `vault_online`; `--online` for **PAM** or **`keeper-vault.v1`** with Commander + folder) |
    21	| `plan` | 0/2/3/4 | `--json` | shape in `AGENTS.md` |
    22	| `diff` | 0/2/3 | – | – |
    23	| `apply` | 0/1/3/4/5 | `--dry-run` (= plan) | per-row outcomes |
    24	| `import` | 0/1/3 | `--dry-run` | adoption plan |
    25	| `export` | 0/1 | `-o FILE` | manifest YAML |
    26	| `bootstrap-ksm` | 0/5/1 | final JSON line | app/record UID prefixes, config path, status |
