   373	- Live smoke matrix is green for supported mutating surfaces.
   374	- Unsupported capabilities fail in validate/plan/apply with clear next actions.
   375	- Docs and scaffold match current behavior.
   376	- GitHub issue state matches current behavior.
   377	
   378	The SDK is not complete if:
